00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:36.850
Captain America: Civil War
The working title of Captain America: Civil

00:00:36.850 --> 00:00:39.000
War was actually "Sputnik".

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:42.449
In the comic books, "Sputnik" was one of the
words used to trigger the Winter Soldier's

00:00:42.449 --> 00:00:43.449
mind control.

00:00:43.449 --> 00:00:45.440
Thor: Ragnarok
Thor: Ragnarok will bring to life a loose

00:00:45.440 --> 00:00:50.519
adaptation of the acclaimed comic book arc
Planet Hulk, and will see Thor and Hulk squaring

00:00:50.519 --> 00:00:55.190
off against each other on a gladiatorial planet,
prior to teaming up to defeat the movie's

00:00:55.190 --> 00:00:56.190
villains.

00:00:56.190 --> 00:00:57.780
Transformers: Age of Extinction
In an interview about Transformers: Age of

00:00:57.780 --> 00:01:02.729
Extinction, director Michael Bay described
the Autobot Hound as "a ballerina with guns".

00:01:02.729 --> 00:01:05.400
This line actually became part of Hound's
dialogue in the movie.

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:08.550
Wolverine (Weapon X)
After 2016's Deadpool became such a huge success

00:01:08.550 --> 00:01:13.440
in spite of it's "R" rating, Fox are intending
to make 2017's Wolverine movie R-rated as

00:01:13.440 --> 00:01:14.440
well.

00:01:14.440 --> 00:01:15.440
Bring on the gore!

00:01:15.440 --> 00:01:17.020
Deadpool
Producer Simon Kinberg has said that Olivia

00:01:17.020 --> 00:01:21.360
Munn auditioned for the role of Vanessa Carlysle
in Deadpool - a role that ultimately went

00:01:21.360 --> 00:01:22.450
to Morena Baccarin.

00:01:22.450 --> 00:01:25.930
However, Munn's audition led to her being
cast as Psylocke in X-Men: Apocalypse.

00:01:25.930 --> 00:01:28.890
X-Men: Apocalypse
In X-Men: Apocalypse, the song playing in

00:01:28.890 --> 00:01:32.609
the scene when Apocalyse finds Angel is by
the heavy metal band Metallica.

00:01:32.609 --> 00:01:37.270
It's called "The Four Horsemen" from the album
"Kill 'Em All", which was released in 1983

00:01:37.270 --> 00:01:38.899
- the same year in which the film takes place.

00:01:38.899 --> 00:01:41.609
The Legend of Tarzan
Alexander SkarsgÃ¥rd was ultimately cast as

00:01:41.609 --> 00:01:45.880
Tarzan in The Legend of Tarzan, but swimmer
Michael Phelps was actually in talks to take

00:01:45.880 --> 00:01:46.880
on the role.

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:50.539
Fellow swimmer Johnny Weissmuller played the
character in the movies of the 1930s and 1940s.

00:01:50.539 --> 00:01:53.700
The Amazing Spider-Man 2
You may recall the scene in The Amazing Spider-Man

00:01:53.700 --> 00:01:56.719
2 in which Gwen Stacy gives a speech at her
graduation.

00:01:56.719 --> 00:01:59.249
Well, actress Emma Stone actually wrote that
speech herself.

00:01:59.249 --> 00:02:01.950
Spider-Man: Homecoming
Marvel Studios head Kevin Feige will be working

00:02:01.950 --> 00:02:04.380
as an Executive Producer on Spider-Man: Homecoming.

00:02:04.380 --> 00:02:08.920
However, unlike when he works on other MCU
movies, Feige will not receive any compensation

00:02:08.920 --> 00:02:11.550
for his role, due to the contract details
in the Marvel/Sony deal.

00:02:11.550 --> 00:02:14.410
Rogue One: A Star Wars Story
John Williams has composed the score for every

00:02:14.410 --> 00:02:18.230
Star Wars theatrical release to date, and
Rogue One will mark the first time in which

00:02:18.230 --> 00:02:19.250
that won't be the case.

00:02:19.250 --> 00:02:21.440
Wonder Woman
Wonder Woman will meet her love interest Steve

00:02:21.440 --> 00:02:23.599
Trevor in her first solo movie.

00:02:23.599 --> 00:02:25.411
In the comic books, they met during World
War II.

00:02:25.411 --> 00:02:26.411
In the movie, they will meet in World War
I.

00:02:26.411 --> 00:02:28.599
The idea is to highlight her immortality more
explicitly.

00:02:28.599 --> 00:02:31.140
Zootopia
In Zootopia, there's a nudist Indian Yoga

00:02:31.140 --> 00:02:34.500
instructor working at Mystic Springs Oasis
named Nangi.

00:02:34.500 --> 00:02:37.680
In India, Nangi refers to a naked woman in
the Hindi language.

00:02:37.680 --> 00:02:40.161
Maleficent
Lana Del Rey sang "Once Upon a Dream" for

00:02:40.161 --> 00:02:42.160
the end credits of Maleficent.

00:02:42.160 --> 00:02:46.540
Del Rey was personally picked by the movie's
star, Angelina Jolie, for the job of doing

00:02:46.540 --> 00:02:47.540
so.

00:02:47.540 --> 00:02:49.260
Batman v Superman: Dawn of Justice
Jeffrey Dean Morgan - who had previously played

00:02:49.260 --> 00:02:54.090
the Comedian in Watchmen - played Bruce Wayne's
Wayne's father Thomas in Batman v Superman,

00:02:54.090 --> 00:02:56.819
but he was actually considered for the role
of Bruce Wayne AKA Batman himself.

00:02:56.819 --> 00:02:59.180
The Martian
One of the key plot elements in The Martian

00:02:59.180 --> 00:03:00.840
is the force of the wind on Mars.

00:03:00.840 --> 00:03:05.269
It is shown as being strong enough to topple
a large rocket and carry big objects.

00:03:05.269 --> 00:03:09.640
In reality, the atmosphere there is so thin,
even the fastest wind would feel like a breeze

00:03:09.640 --> 00:03:12.900
to humans.The Jungle Book
In King Louie's temple in the new Jungle Book

00:03:12.900 --> 00:03:16.420
movie, one of the many treasures he has in
his possessions happens to be the Genie's

00:03:16.420 --> 00:03:17.599
lamp from Aladdin, another Disney movie.

00:03:17.599 --> 00:03:19.730
Warcraft
In spite of its extremely mixed critical reviews,

00:03:19.730 --> 00:03:24.700
with huge takings of $8.5 million, Warcraft
has recently the record for the largest weekday-midnight

00:03:24.700 --> 00:03:25.700
opening in China.

00:03:25.700 --> 00:03:28.099
Avengers: Age of Ultron
For Age of Ultron, in order to make the Scarlet

00:03:28.099 --> 00:03:32.569
Witch's movements look more graceful in action
sequences, actress Elizabeth Olsen worked

00:03:32.569 --> 00:03:33.700
with a dance choreographer.

00:03:33.700 --> 00:03:36.280
Suicide Squad
Although Margot Robbie looks fantastic as

00:03:36.280 --> 00:03:40.290
Harley Quinn in Suicide Squad, Emma Roberts
was actually offered the role first.

00:03:40.290 --> 00:03:43.129
However, she turned it down to star in television's
Scream Queens.

00:03:43.129 --> 00:03:46.470
Suicide Squad
In order to transform Akinnuoye-Agbaje into

00:03:46.470 --> 00:03:50.930
Killer Croc, Suicide Squad's make-up team
took five hours to apply prosthetics to his

00:03:50.930 --> 00:03:52.450
face and upper body.

00:03:52.450 --> 00:03:53.909
The rest was body paint.

